node.text: Giving 'hit the trees' a new meaning, massive switch triple frontflip to the Gucci plateau, and a tranny find gone wrong 😂 Skiers: @martin_hauck, @jonahwilliams, @slickcriminal, & @jasonarens 🎥 @josh_absenger/@_thomasdunzendorfer_, @wearethecoterie, @goodenoughbgk/@lilgthebasedgary

@sivervoll X @snowparkzermatt 👌
↔️ for multiple slides of madness
🤳@anufrievski
